casebody.data:
Vincent, Appellant, v. Preferred Mut. Acc. Ass’n, Respondent. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. May 6, 1889.)

Argued before Larremore, C. J., and Allen and Bookstaver, JJ.

W. B. Kingham, for appellant. Blair & Rudd, for respondent.

Judgment affirmed, with costs. (Memorandum on papers.)
